body_html:
Download eigen (from eigen.tuxfamily.org) and add it in the path, then 'unsupported' directory containing the Eigen/CX11/Tensor will be in the search path. This 'Tensor' file is different one.
But there are a bunch of other files missing, like .pb.h files.
